name: User tries to view the stores by searching with a store name in search bar and if the store is not present

steps.name: I check that the "Stores Screen" is displayed
I verify that the back chevron is present in the search bar
I enter the "Japan" in the "SEARCH BAR" input
I check that the "Search Results Screen" is displayed
I check that the "No stores found" toast message is displayed
